        "content_ViCL9g": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Our commitment",
            "content": "<p>We design and build the Site to align with the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1 at the AA level. That means we work toward:</p><ul><li>Color contrast that’s easy on the eyes</li><li>Text that scales without breaking the layout</li><li>Keyboard navigation across menus, product pages, cart, and checkout</li><li>Alt text on product photography and meaningful imagery</li><li>Clear, descriptive link text and form labels</li><li>Compatibility with the major screen readers</li><li>Captions on video content</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "content_K4VMVf": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Ongoing work",
            "content": "<p>Accessibility isn’t a checkbox — it’s something we keep working on as the Site grows. We test new pages and features for accessibility before they go live, and we re-audit the Site periodically. If we’re falling short somewhere, we want to know.</p>"
          }
        },
        "content_VAX67r": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Tell us if something isn’t working",
            "content": "<p>If you run into an accessibility barrier on the Site, please reach out. Email <a href=\"mailto:hello@tonique.com\" title=\"mailto:hello@tonique.com\">hello@tonique.com</a> with the page you were on and what didn’t work, and we’ll get back to you within five business days. Where we can fix something quickly, we will. Where it’s a bigger lift, we’ll let you know what we’re doing about it.</p>"
          }
        },
        "content_AqWUUF": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Third-party content",
            "content": "<p>Some parts of the Site rely on third-party tools — embedded video, reviews, payment, and similar. We choose vendors that take accessibility seriously, but we can’t guarantee every third-party experience meets the same standard. If a third-party feature is causing a problem, please tell us — we’ll work with the vendor or find another way to give you the same information.</p>"
          }
        },
        "content_FB84tL": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Contact",
            "content": "<p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:hello@tonique.com\" title=\"mailto:hello@tonique.com\">hello@tonique.com</a><br/>Subject line: Accessibility</p>"
          }
        }
